1. L-Listening; Ind-Individual work; CG-Clicker Q discussn; WG-Worksheet group work; OG-Other group work; AnQ-Answer Q; SQ-Student Q; WC-Whole class discuss.; Prd-Predicting; SP-Student present.; TQ-Test/quiz; W-Waiting;  O-Other
2. Lec-Lecturing; RtW-Writing; FUp-Follow-up; PQ-Pose Q; CQ-Clicker Q; AnQ-Answer Q; MG-Moving/Guiding; 1o1-One-on-one; D/V-Demo+; Adm-Admin; W-Waiting; O-Other
For each 2 minute interval, check columns to show what’s happening in each category (or draw vertical line to indicate continuation of activity). Check multiple columns where appropriate.

column30: Comments:  EG: explain difficult coding choices,  flag key points for feedback for the instructor,  identify good analogies, etc.
